WHAT THEY'RE DOING.

447
00:26:05,541 --> 00:26:08,416
- Mako: I'M NOT LOSING
TO THIS CREEP NO MATTER WHAT.

448
00:26:11,583 --> 00:26:13,250
- Sayuki: THIS IS UNREAL.

449
00:26:13,333 --> 00:26:15,541
HER DRIVING IS
COMPLETELY DIFFERENT NOW.

