00:27:22,208 --> 00:27:24,708
WE'RE FINISHING HIM OFF
AT THE NEXT CORNER.

465
00:27:24,791 --> 00:27:26,250
THAT'S C-121.

466
00:27:28,375 --> 00:27:30,041
I'M TELLING YOU SOMETHING
YOU ALREADY KNOW,

467
00:27:30,125 --> 00:27:31,333
BUT YOU'RE A HELL OF
A LOT FASTER

468
00:27:31,416 --> 00:27:32,750
ON THE STRAIGHTAWAYS TONIGHT.

