00:27:32,833 --> 00:27:34,416
NOW YOU'RE GOING TO BE
ENTERING THE CORNER

470
00:27:34,500 --> 00:27:36,416
AT A MUCH HIGHER SPEED
THAN YOU'RE USED TO,

471
00:27:36,500 --> 00:27:37,833
SO DON'T FORGET
TO ADJUST FOR THAT

472
00:27:37,916 --> 00:27:39,000
