00:27:45,166 --> 00:27:46,666
EXCELLENT.
NO CARS AHEAD.

474
00:27:46,750 --> 00:27:48,500
TIME TO NAIL IT.  GO!

475
00:27:57,083 --> 00:27:59,000
- ( grunts )
IF THOSE FREAKING CHICKS

476
00:27:59,083 --> 00:28:00,416
CAN CLEAR THAT CORNER
THAT EASY,

477
00:28:00,500 --> 00:28:02,333
THEN MY EVO FOUR
CAN DO IT NO SWEAT.

478
00:28:02,416 --> 00:28:03,458
HERE I COME!

479
00:28:21,291 --> 00:28:22,791
I'M GOING TOO WIDE.

480
00:28:22,875 --> 00:28:24,208
I CAN'T STAY ON
THE SAME LINE. 

481
00:28:24,291 --> 00:28:25,166
I'M GONNA CRASH!

482
00:28:29,666 --> 00:28:30,541
