00:29:42,583 --> 00:29:45,041
- WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT, DUDE?

499
00:29:45,125 --> 00:29:46,875
WE BEAT THEIR ASSES.

500
00:29:46,958 --> 00:29:48,958
- ( both gasp )

501
00:29:49,041 --> 00:29:52,875
- I SAID WE WHIPPED 
THEIR TAILS, STUPID.

502
00:29:56,458 --> 00:29:58,333
- Shingo and Takeshi:
THEY WON?!

503
00:29:59,958 --> 00:30:02,208
- MAKO WAS REALLY
SHINING TONIGHT. 

504
00:30:02,291 --> 00:30:04,708
