BEHIND THE WHEEL.

505
00:30:04,791 --> 00:30:06,125
- CUT IT OUT.

506
00:30:06,208 --> 00:30:07,625
- ( giggles )

507
00:30:07,708 --> 00:30:09,583
LET'S GET OUT OF HERE.

508
00:30:11,208 --> 00:30:13,083
SEE YOU AROUND, SHINGO.

509
00:30:16,958 --> 00:30:19,666
- HEY, WAIT.  YOU KNOW,
WE CAME ALL THE WAY OUT HERE

510
00:30:19,750 --> 00:30:22,083
TO ROOT FOR YOU AND NOW
YOU'RE JUST GONNA RUN AWAY?

511
00:30:22,166 --> 00:30:23,041
- ( engine starts )

512
00:30:30,833 --> 00:30:33,791
- DUDE, THAT SIL-EIGHTY IS
GIVING OFF SOME SERIOUS VIBES,

513
00:30:33,875 --> 00:30:34,750
I SWEAR.

514
00:30:34,833 --> 00:30:36,916
THOSE CHICKS ARE
THE REAL DEAL.

515
00:30:54,833 --> 00:30:56,916
- YOU ROCKED IT OUT
LAST NIGHT, MAKO.

516
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:59,500
- I DON'T KNOW. MAYBE THE GUY
DRIVING THE LAN-EVO LAST NIGHT

517
00:30:59,583 --> 00:31:01,208
WASN'T REALLY THAT
GOOD OF A RACER.

