00:34:23,791 --> 00:34:26,125
OF COURSE IT WAS
THE EXACT SAME STORY

582
00:34:26,208 --> 00:34:28,291
WHEN YOU FIRST STARTED
LEARNING HOW TO DRIFT.

583
00:34:28,375 --> 00:34:29,916
