00:34:34,083 --> 00:34:35,833
( laughs )
IT'S SHINGO!

586
00:34:35,916 --> 00:34:37,333
WHAT'S HE DOING HERE?

587
00:34:37,416 --> 00:34:40,208
- OH, HEY.
WHAT'S UP, SAYUKI?

588
00:34:40,291 --> 00:34:42,250
- LONG TIME NO SEE, MAN.

589
00:34:42,333 --> 00:34:45,166
IT'S CRAZY TO RUN INTO YOU
ALL THE WAY UP ON THIS MOUNTAIN.

590
00:34:45,250 --> 00:34:48,166
I HAD NO IDEA THAT
YOU WERE INTO SNOWBOARDING.

591
00:34:48,250 --> 00:34:50,000
- YEAH.  I DIG IT.

592
00:34:50,083 --> 00:34:51,916
IT'S MY THING.
- THAT'S AWESOME.

593
00:34:52,000 --> 00:34:54,000
AGAIN, I HAD NO IDEA.

594
00:34:54,083 --> 00:34:55,250
- ( Shingo and Sayuki chuckle )

595
00:34:55,333 --> 00:34:56,583
- Shingo: COME ON, I KNOW
HOW TO SNOWBOARD.

596
00:34:56,666 --> 00:34:58,541
PRETTY FREAKING GOOD TOO.

597
00:34:58,625 --> 00:35:01,750
- Sayuki: AND IN GRADE SCHOOL,
SHINGO ALWAYS HAD A STREAM OF 

598
00:35:01,833 --> 00:35:03,166
