00:35:10,416 --> 00:35:12,791
AND TURNED INTO A SLICK BOY
REBEL RACER, RIGHT?

604
00:35:12,875 --> 00:35:14,791
- DON'T GO MAKING
STUFF UP, SAYUKI.

605
00:35:14,875 --> 00:35:17,708
COME ON. I JUST HAD A BUTTLOAD
OF ALLERGIES WHEN I WAS A KID.

606
00:35:17,791 --> 00:35:19,000
YOU KNOW THAT.

607
00:35:19,083 --> 00:35:21,625
- ( chuckles )

608
00:35:21,708 --> 00:35:24,625
SO MAKO, WANT TO GET OUT THERE
AND HIT THE SLOPES A BIT MORE?

609
00:35:24,708 --> 00:35:26,458
- UH...
- GO ON, I DON'T MIND.

610
00:35:26,541 --> 00:35:28,875
I THINK I'M GONNA STAY HERE
AND CATCH UP WITH SHINGO A BIT.

611
00:35:28,958 --> 00:35:30,458
TALK ABOUT THE GOOD OLD DAYS.

612
00:35:30,541 --> 00:35:32,208
HEY, WHY DON'T YOU GO UP
WITH HER, MIYAHARA?

613
00:35:32,291 --> 00:35:34,166
IT'LL BE FUN.
- ( gasps )

614
00:35:34,250 --> 00:35:36,375
- SURE.  I COULD GO
FOR ANOTHER RUN.

615
00:35:36,458 --> 00:35:38,875
- YEAH.  I COULD
USE THE COMPANY.

616
00:35:38,958 --> 00:35:41,583
- YOU GOT IT.

617
00:35:41,666 --> 00:35:44,541
- ( people chattering )

618
00:35:46,041 --> 00:35:47,625
- Shingo:
SO WHAT DO YOU THINK OF HIM?

619
00:35:47,708 --> 00:35:49,375
- HE KIND OF
LOOKS LIKE A WHIMP,

620
00:35:49,458 --> 00:35:52,208
