I GOTTA SAY, HE SEEMS NORMAL.

621
00:35:52,291 --> 00:35:54,583
ANY IDEA HOW
HIS DRIVING IS?

622
00:35:54,666 --> 00:35:57,166
- HE'S ONE OF THE FASTER
DRIVERS THE NIGHT KIDS HAVE.

623
00:35:57,250 --> 00:35:59,916
BUT OF COURSE, NOT AS FAST
AS A COUPLE CHICKS I KNOW 

624
00:36:00,000 --> 00:36:02,166
WHO DRIVE A RIDE
CALLED IMPACT BLUE.

625
00:36:02,250 --> 00:36:04,333
- ( chuckles )

626
00:36:04,416 --> 00:36:06,250
- ( sighs )

627
00:36:06,333 --> 00:36:07,833
YOU KNOW,
SPEAKING OF FRIENDS,

628
00:36:07,916 --> 00:36:10,250
YOURS IS TOO CUTE
NOT TO HAVE A BOYFRIEND.

629
00:36:10,333 --> 00:36:12,250
I DON'T KNOW WHY YOU DIDN'T
TRY TO HOOK YOUR BUDDY SHINGO

630
00:36:12,333 --> 00:36:13,458
