BY THE WAY, IF YOU LET
THE CAT OUT OF THE BAG

634
00:36:19,416 --> 00:36:20,833
AND TELL EITHER OF THEM
THAT THIS WAS

635
00:36:20,916 --> 00:36:22,500
A BLIND DATE SETUP,
SHE'LL KILL ME

636
00:36:22,583 --> 00:36:24,500
